*xchat-1.9.3-r3.ebuild (02 Nov 2002)

  02 Nov 2002; foser <foser@gentoo.org> xchat-1.9.3-r3.ebuild :
  Fixed launcher
  Added tint transparancy patch
  Added option for disabling xft (bug #9973)

*xchat-1.9.3-r2.ebuild (20 Oct 2002)

  20 Oct 2002; foser <foser@gentoo.org> xchat-1.9.3-r2.ebuild :
  Now really fixing plugins 
  Added a patch to prevent problems with gnome2.1 and up

*xchat-1.9.3-r1.ebuild (11 Oct 2002)

  11 Oct 2002; Brandon Low <lostlogic@gentoo.org> xchat-1.9.3-r1.ebuild:

